Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:24.13,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}平凡无奇地度过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.14,0:00:28.79,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}怀着无数问号
