Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.64,0:00:53.13,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}这阵风的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:58.82,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}定会有真实的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.90,0:01:00.73,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.80,0:01:03.34,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}这些泪水
