Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.94,0:01:13.03,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}即使现在还很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.11,0:01:18.17,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}即使现在还很遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.27,0:01:22.22,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}只需微微一笑
