Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.17,0:22:46.56,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}隔着玻璃晃过的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.60,0:22:48.46,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}那忧伤的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.59,0:22:54.80,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}距离那么近 却无法触及
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.98,0:22:59.27,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}积累种种借口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.42,0:23:02.12,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}逃避着现在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.23,0:23:10.14,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}那时几近崩溃的软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.31,0:23:13.49,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}此刻仿佛已能面对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:15.17,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}Love in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.21,0:23:17.60,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}打开门扉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.72,0:23:21.08,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}前往有你的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.22,0:23:28.15,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}告诉你这份焦灼已久的心情
