Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.76,0:01:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.45,0:01:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然停了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真稀奇啊 还用怀表？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.15,0:01:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是特别的日子 所以找出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.71,0:02:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别的日子…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这岛上有钟表店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁止当我们这儿是孤岛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓人君还没去过商店街那边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.35,0:02:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在今天之内修好它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.04,0:02:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我今天就带你上街吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.44,0:02:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤岛的街啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 今天我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.93,0:02:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用管我 你们俩玩得开心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.86,0:02:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天来约会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.73,0:03:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来 那怀表为什么一定要今天修好？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.31,0:03:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 有点原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那像木头棒子似的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 那是防身棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防身棒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都这么叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是碰到毒蛇就用那棒子吓走它免得被咬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 还真有孤岛风范
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.66,0:03:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 居高临下的口气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.98,0:03:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 竟然有剧场还有新潮的书店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.07,0:03:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想买色情杂志的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我在外面等吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐呐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否决
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副部长？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有何收获啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外乡人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扰乱岛上秩序的人 决不原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐呐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那衬衫 蛮适合须方的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天 是须方君的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 须方君不喜欢过生日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「须方」是进藤家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:05:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每代生就带有印记的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能取的特别的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方君知道自己的身世和素体的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好是5年前的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那以后 他好像就很讨厌自己的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方也能驾驶素体？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方君的 有点不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tauburn那些是战士的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我继承的是巫女的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 进藤家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方君继承的是王的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:41.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其力量大概是这个星球最强的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最强的素体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那台素体多半坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不能动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是不能驾驶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,素体虽然不能动 却可以驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.94,0:07:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.07,0:07:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驭者将会获得强力的第一阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.34,0:07:20.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一阶段…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈子夫人的背部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.46,0:07:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的姿色和商业才能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是第一阶段的力量哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是这样也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由驯化产生的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在零时空间以外也能使用的素体之力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是第一阶段的定义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:08:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不一定是超常现象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在社会上突然大获成功的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:07.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能是将第一阶段的力量据为己有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.29,0:08:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能如果被社会认同也算幸福的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,异能的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许只会让持有者遭遇不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和巫女的我不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方同学想离开是可以离开岛的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是为了避免那强大的力量在外部使用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方君也被禁止离开岛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被这孤岛所困
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方拥有什么力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.53,0:08:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.45,0:08:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然拥有印记
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是须方君没有驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驯化王之素体的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下记录的几乎所有驾驭者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:08:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在使用了被称为王之柱的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强力第一阶段力量之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陷入深沉的睡眠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也没有醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薄荷茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.86,0:09:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薄荷茶是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请稍候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那个轻浮女和那外乡人发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会失去巫女的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能坐视计划继续被拖延了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还无法控制自己的第一阶段吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰别人谈恋爱就太不解风情了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你在陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.98,0:10:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.39,0:10:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.55,0:10:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢他对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我而言是重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和须方君 从小相识
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出生在这里的皆水神社
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继承了封印巫女的印记
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得知命中注定无法离开岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.43,0:11:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却能坚持到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多半是因为有背负着同样命运的须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪伴在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.81,0:11:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方君 总是随身携带着小刀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么带着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直害怕 不敢问
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候须方君生日宴会上的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他戴着我送的玻璃珠项链
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别提多高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 笑得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是他的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却不能对他说生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,礼物也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每年在其他日子 找其他理由送出
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 今天我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.11,0:12:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用管我 你们俩玩得开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的生日成为讨厌的纪念日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定很伤心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想利用拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为他庆祝生日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这座岛上要有素体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我们要生在这岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在去把礼物交给须方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:13:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爷今天不见任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把自己一个人关在道场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 和子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里应该可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.72,0:13:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方在不在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 有须方君的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 这是我给须方的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 也是给自己的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.07,0:13:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这儿唱首歌好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险又漆黑的夜海上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨姆手持鱼叉 发起挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在无法用语言叙述的激烈战斗过后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死乌贼大王的萨姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.57,0:14:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于获得了那青色的血液
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 没有战斗场景描写吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乌贼大王的青色血液
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.15,0:15:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在瓶中煌煌生辉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照亮了夜色的大海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充满神秘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着这瓶青色的血液
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.32,0:15:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨姆得以晋见国王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国王大人 这是约定的青色血液
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国王激动得浑身发抖 接过瓶子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口喝下了那瓶青色液体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那青色的血液
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被施以不老不死的国王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用来结束他永恒人生的唯一解药
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 萨姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今夜入眠后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.85,0:15:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我便也不会再次醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:15:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出乎意料的剧情展开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这果汁 不好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢 萨姆怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人生的冒险仍在继续…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吊人胃口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游弋吧 美人鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.59,0:17:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等前来相助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆水大人请隐蔽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和子躲好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防身棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么 温蒂尼（Ondine）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.10,0:18:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 犯规也得有个限度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用它 拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来得好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豪快 银河十文字斩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了 温蒂尼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.77,0:19:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外乡人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美人鱼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想让它做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆水巫女也在那里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.93,0:19:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是美人鱼自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没停下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.63,0:19:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深层意识的暴走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.92,0:20:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,it's a pinch
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.04,0:20:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开和子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:20:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柱！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王之柱…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:21:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方君！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.67,0:22:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.94,0:22:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方君 须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.35,0:22:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒醒 醒醒啊
